&lt;p&gt;The Senior Director of Market Development plays a strategic leadership role in expanding the company’s footprint identifying, developing, and accelerating growth opportunities in new and existing markets in support of EdgeConneX’s global expansion plans. This role combines strategic thinking with hands-on execution, working cross-functionally to identify opportunities, understand trends, develop recommendations about, and bring to life market opportunities that align with the company’s growth objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a proven, self-starter who will collaborate with Regional leads, Sales, Marketing, Engineering, and Customer Solutions teams to recommend opportunities to the Executive Team that ensure that the company remains competitive and responsive to changing market dynamics globally. The successful candidate’s efforts will be geared towards creating sustainable growth avenues, enhancing the company’s position, and – ultimately – driving revenue. This position will primarily act as an advisor to the Managing Director, EMEA and report to the SVP, Sales Enablement.&lt;/p&gt;
