&lt;p&gt;Evaluate potential markets and development projects, assessing their feasibility, profitability, and alignment with the company&#39;s investment strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform market intelligence analyses in support of identified new markets. Track and analyze market trends in AI-driven compute demand, power procurement, data center supply/demand dynamics, and regulatory development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define and drive market development strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support go-to-market planning for new market entry, including market sizing, site selection dynamics, power availability, competitive positioning, and business case development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage strategic partnerships and relationships with key internal stakeholders. Collaborate with Country Managers, Real Estate, Site Development, Power, Product, Sales, Finance, Marketing, Engineering, Operations, and partners to align market development initiatives with company priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and present executive-level recommendations and updates on market strategy and investment recommendations to Executive leadership and investment committees.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive regular regional coordination and prepare weekly reviews for Managing Director EMEA and Quarterly Regional Strategy Reviews for Executive Team and outside investors.&lt;/li&g

